reviewText: I wish this series was available in the North American viewing format, as it is one of the funniest shows ever.  I purchased an all region DVD player just to watch this series.  It is laugh out loud hilarious.

I recently had a vacation to London, England and my friend got me to watch this British comedy called Benidorm.  It was so funny that I've ordered a multi-regional dvd player since it only comes in region 2.  But it is all worth it.  I know you be laughing for hours of great British humor.

Skylar
